data.description:
Beautifully Renovated Property in Canyon, TX 
This stunning property has recently undergone a renovation, complete with fresh carpeting and new paint. Located in the heart of Canyon, TX, this spacious home boasts four bedrooms, two bathrooms, a dining room, two living areas (or ideal office space), a two-car garage, and a large backyard. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, including double ovens, a five-burner gas cooktop, and a refrigerator that is included with the property. This home is perfect for a large family or as a college rental, as it's located near WTAMU, restaurants, and other activities. The seller is even willing to provide a one-year home warranty with an acceptable offer. Contact us today to schedule a private showing.
